.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
Color: blood-red, ebony, purple, azure, orange
Nationality: colombian, polish, indian, nigerian, egyptian
Cigar: cain, vegafina, dannemann, davidoff, old-henry
Beverage: juice, fanta, mirinda, almond-milk, hot-chocolate
Pet: frog, hedgehog, hamster, goat, mouse

1. Nationality:colombian == Color:blood-red
2. Nationality:polish == Pet:frog
3. Beverage:juice == Color:ebony
4. Nationality:indian == Beverage:fanta
5. Color:ebony is to the right of Color:purple
6. Cigar:cain == Pet:mouse
7. Cigar:vegafina == Color:azure
8. Beverage:mirinda is in the middle
9. Nationality:nigerian is on the far left
10. Cigar:dannemann is on the left or right of Pet:hedgehog
11. Cigar:vegafina is to the left or right of Pet:goat
12. Cigar:davidoff == Beverage:almond-milk
13. Nationality:egyptian == Cigar:old-henry
14. Nationality:nigerian is to the left or right of Color:orange

